{
    "name": "Boar",
    "type": "creature",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Boar",
            "type": "section",
            "text": "Boars are omnivorous mammals, hunted heavily because their meat is considered a delicacy. Boars are most likely to attack humanoids either in self-defense or during their mating season in the winter months, when the males grow an extra inch of tissue to protect their organs as they fight off rivals. Of course, in some cultures, boars are trained to become much more aggressive so they can fill the roles of warbeast and guardian. When such boars escape back into the wild, they can become true terrors in the region.",
            "sources": [
                {
                    "type": "source",
                    "name": "Monster Core",
                    "link": {
                        "type": "link",
                        "name": "Monster Core pg. 43",
                        "alt": "Monster Core pg. 43",
                        "game-obj": "Sources",
                        "aonid": 221
                    },
                    "page": 43,
                    "errata": {
                        "type": "link",
                        "name": "1.1",
                        "alt": "1.1",
                        "game-obj": "Sources",
                        "aonid": 221
                    }
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "Boar",
            "type": "section",
            "sections": [
                {
                    "name": "Boar Territory",
                    "type": "section",
                    "text": "Boars can be found in almost any environment, from forests to deserts, warm or cold, including even highaltitude mountainous regions. They tend to prefer forests, marshes, and meadows. Daeodons are likewise found in such regions but generally prefer remote reaches far from civilization.",
                    "sources": [
                        {
                            "type": "source",
                            "name": "Monster Core",
                            "link": {
                                "type": "link",
                                "name": "Monster Core pg. 43",
                                "alt": "Monster Core pg. 43",
                                "game-obj": "Sources",
                                "aonid": 221
                            },
                            "page": 43,
                            "errata": {
                                "type": "link",
                                "name": "1.1",
                                "alt": "1.1",
                                "game-obj": "Sources",
                                "aonid": 221
                            }
                        }
                    ],
                    "subtype": "sidebar",
                    "sidebar_type": "locations",
                    "sidebar_heading": "Locations",
                    "image": {
                        "type": "image",
                        "name": "Locations",
                        "image": "Sidebar_3_Locations.png"
                    }
                },
                {
                    "name": "Meat and Hide",
                    "type": "section",
                    "text": "A boar's carcass typically provides enough meat for 100 meals or more, as well as hide and bristles that can be used for crafting.",
                    "sources": [
                        {
                            "type": "source",
                            "name": "Monster Core",
                            "link": {
                                "type": "link",
                                "name": "Monster Core pg. 43",
                                "alt": "Monster Core pg. 43",
                                "game-obj": "Sources",
                                "aonid": 221
                            },
                            "page": 43,
                            "errata": {
                                "type": "link",
                                "name": "1.1",
                                "alt": "1.1",
                                "game-obj": "Sources",
                                "aonid": 221
                            }
                        }
                    ],
                    "subtype": "sidebar",
                    "sidebar_type": "treasure_and_rewards",
                    "sidebar_heading": "Treasure and Rewards",
                    "image": {
                        "type": "image",
                        "name": "Treasure and Rewards",
                        "image": "Sidebar_5_TreasureAndRewards.png"
                    }
                }
            ],
            "text": "While domesticated pigs are a staple of farm life, wild boars are much more dangerous. Foul-tempered warthogs are relatively common, while the lumbering, primeval beasts known as daeodons are less so. Voracious boars can ravage the countryside in which they live, making them a particular nuisance to farmers. Boars breed freely, and a pair of boars can rapidly grow to a large family.",
            "sources": [
                {
                    "type": "source",
                    "name": "Monster Core",
                    "link": {
                        "type": "link",
                        "name": "Monster Core pg. 43",
                        "alt": "Monster Core pg. 43",
                        "game-obj": "Sources",
